{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.014.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Z\u00e8le du roi Asa pour la destruction de l\u2019idol\u00e2trie<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. 1 S 12:7-15, 20-25. \u00c9s 3:10. Os 10:12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>L\u2019esprit de Dieu fut sur Azaria, fils d\u2019Obed,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.2","name":"2 Chroniques 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.14.14","name":"2 Chroniques 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.14.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>et Azaria alla au-devant d\u2019Asa et lui dit: \u00c9coutez-moi, Asa, et tout Juda et Benjamin! L\u2019\u00c9ternel est avec vous quand vous \u00eates avec lui; si vous le cherchez, vous le trouverez; mais si vous l\u2019abandonnez, il vous abandonnera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.3","name":"2 Chroniques 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.1","name":"2 Chroniques 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Pendant longtemps il n\u2019y a eu pour Isra\u00ebl ni vrai Dieu, ni sacrificateur qui enseign\u00e2t, ni loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.4","name":"2 Chroniques 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.2","name":"2 Chroniques 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mais au sein de leur d\u00e9tresse ils sont retourn\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, ils l\u2019ont cherch\u00e9, et ils l\u2019ont trouv\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.5","name":"2 Chroniques 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.3","name":"2 Chroniques 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Dans ces temps-l\u00e0, point de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 pour ceux qui allaient et venaient, car il y avait de grands troubles parmi tous les habitants du pays;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.6","name":"2 Chroniques 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.4","name":"2 Chroniques 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>on se heurtait peuple contre peuple, ville contre ville, parce que Dieu les agitait par toutes sortes d\u2019angoisses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.7","name":"2 Chroniques 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.5","name":"2 Chroniques 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Vous donc, fortifiez-vous, et ne laissez pas vos mains s\u2019affaiblir, car il y aura un salaire pour vos \u0153uvres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.8","name":"2 Chroniques 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.6","name":"2 Chroniques 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-19: cf. 1 R 15:11-15. 2 R 23:1-7. \u00c9s 26:3, 4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir entendu ces paroles et la proph\u00e9tie d\u2019Obed le proph\u00e8te, Asa se fortifia et fit dispara\u00eetre les abominations de tout le pays de Juda et de Benjamin et des villes qu\u2019il avait prises dans la montagne d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, et il restaura l\u2019autel de l\u2019\u00c9ternel qui \u00e9tait devant le portique de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.9","name":"2 Chroniques 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.7","name":"2 Chroniques 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il rassembla tout Juda et Benjamin, et ceux d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, de Manass\u00e9 et de Sim\u00e9on qui habitaient parmi eux, car un grand nombre de gens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl se joignirent \u00e0 lui lorsqu\u2019ils virent que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, \u00e9tait avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.10","name":"2 Chroniques 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.8","name":"2 Chroniques 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ils s\u2019assembl\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem le troisi\u00e8me mois de la quinzi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du r\u00e8gne d\u2019Asa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.11","name":"2 Chroniques 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.9","name":"2 Chroniques 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Ce jour-l\u00e0, ils sacrifi\u00e8rent \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, sur le butin qu\u2019ils avaient amen\u00e9, sept cents b\u0153ufs et sept mille brebis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.12","name":"2 Chroniques 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.10","name":"2 Chroniques 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ils prirent l\u2019engagement de chercher l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res, de tout leur c\u0153ur et de toute leur \u00e2me;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.13","name":"2 Chroniques 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.11","name":"2 Chroniques 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>et quiconque ne chercherait pas l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, devait \u00eatre mis \u00e0 mort, petit ou grand, homme ou femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.14","name":"2 Chroniques 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.12","name":"2 Chroniques 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ils jur\u00e8rent fid\u00e9lit\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 voix haute, avec des cris de joie, et au son des trompettes et des cors;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.13","name":"2 Chroniques 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>tout Juda se r\u00e9jouit de ce serment, car ils avaient jur\u00e9 de tout leur c\u0153ur, ils avaient cherch\u00e9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel de plein gr\u00e9, et ils l\u2019avaient trouv\u00e9, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel leur donna du repos de tous c\u00f4t\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.16","name":"2 Chroniques 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.14","name":"2 Chroniques 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le roi Asa enleva m\u00eame \u00e0 Maaca, sa m\u00e8re, la dignit\u00e9 de reine, parce qu\u2019elle avait fait une idole pour Astart\u00e9. Asa abattit son idole, qu\u2019il r\u00e9duisit en poussi\u00e8re, et la br\u00fbla au torrent de C\u00e9dron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.17","name":"2 Chroniques 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Mais les hauts lieux ne disparurent point d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, quoique le c\u0153ur d\u2019Asa f\u00fbt en entier \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel pendant toute sa vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.18","name":"2 Chroniques 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.16","name":"2 Chroniques 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il mit dans la maison de Dieu les choses consacr\u00e9es par son p\u00e8re et par lui-m\u00eame, de l\u2019argent, de l\u2019or et des vases.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.19","name":"2 Chroniques 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.17","name":"2 Chroniques 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 15:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Il n\u2019y eut point de guerre jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la trente-cinqui\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du r\u00e8gne d\u2019Asa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15","name":"2 Chroniques 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.16.1","name":"2 Chroniques 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.15.18","name":"2 Chroniques 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar 